FBIS3-10957 "drlat050_b_94007" FBIS-LAT-94-050 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Mar 1994 Haiti Employers Groups Urge Senators To `Regain Control' FL1403221194 Port-au-Prince Radio Metropole in French 1700 GMT 14 Mar 94 FL1403221194 Port-au-Prince Radio Metropole Language: French Article Type:BFN [Text] Haitian employers associations are urging the senators to regain control of themselves and quickly put an end to their quarrel. They ask that they resume acting with wisdom, maturity, and patriotism to extract the country from this destructive mess into which it sinks a little more deeply each day.
